						               													<description>&amp;quot;Commissioner, we were able to establish contact with a crown witness! But she is suspicious and asking for proof.&amp;#10;She won&amp;lsquo;t tell us anything without assurances that we are actually investigating this case!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;The Crown Witness&amp;quot; is an additional variant for &amp;quot;The Key &amp;ndash; Theft in Cliffrock Villa&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a mini expansion for the very first &amp;quot;The Key&amp;quot; Game. It was a free promo on Spiel Essen 2022 and consists of 30 Cards: 6 rule cards, 6 Questions and 18 hints.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Promo adds a new aspect to the game: At the start of the game one card is drawn that lets the crown witness ask a question concerning the case.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;When playing you can focus to answer that question. When you can answer it, you note the answer and take a free info. only if you are last to answer, you get nothing.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It therefore adds a little race at the start of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
